commentText: Indicates whether the given type can be read by this converter._This method should perform the same checks than_{@link HttpMessageConverter#canRead(Class, MediaType)} with additional ones_related to the generic type._@param type the (potentially generic) type to test for readability_@param contextClass a context class for the target type, for example a class_in which the target type appears in a method signature (can be {@code null})_@param mediaType the media type to read, can be {@code null} if not specified._Typically the value of a {@code Content-Type} header._@return {@code true} if readable_ {@code false} otherwise
codeText: boolean canRead(Type type, @Nullable Class<?> contextClass, @Nullable MediaType mediaType)_
